snippet.title: [Studio Pixel] Rockfish demo ver. 111127 playthrough
snippet.description:
Download the game: https://studiopixel.jp/binaries/RockfishExe111127-ron.zip
On July 30th, 2023, Pixel released the demo of Rockfish on his Discord server. This is the first iteration of Rockfish, it was redone once before ultimately being cancelled in 2012.

Pixel's discord (QVGA): https://discord.com/invite/UQqKn7tHsp
